"weapon.description.lancer" = "Nicknamed Retro Lancer during the Lambent Pandemic, it was the predecessor to the Lancer Mark 2 assault rifle. Formerly the primary assault rifle of the Coalition of Ordered Governments' army, the Mark 1 assault rifle was used during the Pendulum Wars.";
"weapon.name.lancer2" = "Lancer Mark 2 Assault Rifle";
